ry artery sarcomas</article-title><source>Eur Respir J</source><year>2010</year><volume>35</volume><fpage>444</fpage><lpage>6</lpage><pub-id pub-id-type="pmid">20123849</pub-id></element-citation></ref><ref id="ref10"><label>10</label><element-citation publication-type="journal"><person-group person-group-type="author"><name><surname>Benz</surname><given-names>MR</given-names></name><name><surname>Tchekmedyian</surname><given-names>N</given-names></name><name><surname>Eilber</surname><given-names>FC</given-names></name><name><surname>Federman</surname><given-names>N</given-names></name><name><surname>Czernin</surname><given-names>J</given-names></name><name><surname>Tap</surname><given-names>WD</given-names></name></person-group><article-title>Utilization of positron emission tomography in the management of patients with sarcoma</article-title><source>Curr Opin Oncol</source><year>2009</year><volume>21</volume><fpage>345</fpage><lpage>51</lpage><pub-id pub-id-type="pmid">19412096</pub-id></element-citation></ref></ref-list></back></article>